{"tid":1216098,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］駐英大使指中央從未指示港府修例","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T09:04:43.000Z","uid":23299,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"897a0ae0846f21e416683e25625cb36dde59405a","tid":1216098,"uid":23299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:02:16.000Z","msg":"中國駐英國大使劉曉明接受英國媒體訪問時表示，北京從未指示香港修訂《逃犯條例》，修例只是港府因應台灣殺人案而發起，其目的為堵塞現時法例之漏洞。  劉曉明又指，港人上街反對修例是錯誤，是媒體把事件曲解成中央指示港府修例。他認為這是香港內部和外部的一些勢力，在利用此事來挑起事端。  對於香港警方暴力對付示威者，劉曉明表示開始時只是和平遊行，但後來變得很惡劣，當示威者襲擊警察，警察便要自衞。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-13-2019/53607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-13-2019%2F53607&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmYvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=1358ee05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-13-2019/53607</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-13-2019/53607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-13-2019%2F53607&d=BSpFugi7VYdA%2F48z81zRmYvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=1358ee05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-13-2019/53607</a>"},{"pid":"4360a4dbdeb00e67f607cc48a7ab156a0a24579b","tid":1216098,"uid":23299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:04:43.000Z","msg":"Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}